Mid 1 and Mid 2 in one Folder:
To start application you can just type docker compose up

urls for Mid 2:

localhost:8080/item/find?name=&rating=2-5&price=0-100- GET endpoint for filtration by 3 parameters, as you wish

localhost:8080/comment/add - post endpoint for adding comments 
{
    "item_id":1,
    "user_id": 2,
    "content": "Збс яблочки",
    "parent_id": 1
} - request body


localhost:8080/rating/add - adding rating to items - post endpoint

{
    "item_id":1,
    "user_id": 2,
    "rating": 5
}
